                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840526-7-off42 t17840526-7-cd43"></join> last, six live hens, price 6 s. one live cock, value 2 s. five live ducks, value 4 s. and four eggs, value 2 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
